    • Method Detail

      • initialize

        public void initialize()
        This method initializes the GUI by setting the region to that of the connected user, initializing the array arrStr, and setting the recievedData flag to false. It then sends a message to the chat object with a request for a list of machines in the user's region, and sets up the combo box with the data received. It also sends a message to the chat object with a request for a list of supply workers and sets up the combo box with the data received.
        Specified by:
        initialize in interface IScreen
        Throws:
        java.lang.Exception - if an error occurs while initializing the GUI.
